description: AMUNDI PRIME EMERGING MARKETS UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, the performance of Solactive GBS Emerging Markets Large & Mid Cap USD Index (Net Total return) whether it is rising or falling. This ETF offers exposure to large and mid-cap stocks across 26 Emerging countries. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus or www.solactive.com.
name: Amundi Prime Emerging Markets UCITS ETF DR (C)
